import React from 'react'
import { ChakraProvider, Box, Text } from "@chakra-ui/react"

const Logo = (props) => {
    return (
        <ChakraProvider>
            <Box {...props}>
                <Text fontSize="lg" fontWeight="bold">
                    Logo
                </Text>
            </Box>
        </ChakraProvider>
    )
}

export default Logo
